[[span class="h-span"]]Authors:[[/span]] [[*user Lt Flops]] and KindlyTurtleClem 

This article is **FIRE TURTLE (Clem & Floppy)**'s 2nd article for the **[*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/collaboration-contest 2019 Collaboration Contest]**! **[*https:/scp-wiki.wikidot.com/land-of-honey Go here for the first entry!]** The two primary Groups of Interest featured are **Fifthism** and **Church of the Second Hytoth**. 

This article shares continuity with **[*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-3739 SCP-3739]**. However, you do not need to read 3739 to understand 4475! 
----
