4. [[span class="h-span" style="text-decoration: underline;"]]EQUIPMENT[[/span]] CRIMSON COWBELL personnel charged with SCP-4475 exploration have been granted the following equipment and materials:
* Three pressurized VISTA-Type Extravehicular Mobility Unit support suits, each outfitted with a SCRAMBLE headset[[footnote]][[span class="h-span"]]SCRAMBLE:[[/span]] An audiovisual program that provides simultaneous recording and memetihazard filtering.[[/footnote]] and 30 hours of oxygen.
